App for vizualization isometric rotation of shapes(pseudo 3d). Written with GTK.

conception:
you can choose form: cube or sphere(icosahedrone)
you can edit size(scale-up/scale-down)
you can edit horizontal rotation(left/right)
you can edit vertical rotation(up/down)

structure of code:
-global:
--int array matrix[12][3] matrix_projection[12][2]
--int koefficients:
---ks - size
---kw - width
---kh - height
-initialization control functions
-activation function:
--get builder(window,scales,buttons)
--set draw frame(and attach draw function)
--show window
-main function:
--context and attach activation
-control functions:
--draw function
---make projection from matrix to matrix_projection
---if cube then load cairo for cube
---if sphere then load cairo for sphere
--button sphere function
--button cube function
--scale size function
--scale horizontal rotation function
--scale vertical rotation function
